23#include "mpfr-impl.h"
24
25static int
26mpfr_fmma_aux (mpfr_ptr z, mpfr_srcptr a, mpfr_srcptr b, mpfr_srcptr c,
27 mpfr_srcptr d, mpfr_rnd_t rnd, int neg)
28{
29 mpfr_ubf_t u, v;
30 mpfr_t zz;
31 mpfr_prec_t prec_z = MPFR_PREC(z);
32 mp_size_t un, vn;
33 mpfr_limb_ptr up, vp, zp;
34 int inex;
35 MPFR_TMP_DECL(marker);
36
37 MPFR_LOG_FUNC
38 (("a[%Pu]=%.*Rg b[%Pu]=%.*Rg c[%Pu]=%.*Rg d[%Pu]=%.*Rg rnd=%d neg=%d",
39 mpfr_get_prec (a), mpfr_log_prec, a,
40 mpfr_get_prec (b), mpfr_log_prec, b,
41 mpfr_get_prec (c), mpfr_log_prec, c,
42 mpfr_get_prec (d), mpfr_log_prec, d, rnd, neg),
43 ("z[%Pu]=%.*Rg inex=%d",
44 mpfr_get_prec (z), mpfr_log_prec, z, inex));
45
46 MPFR_TMP_MARK (marker);
47
48 un = MPFR_LIMB_SIZE (a) + MPFR_LIMB_SIZE (b);
49 vn = MPFR_LIMB_SIZE (c) + MPFR_LIMB_SIZE (d);
50 MPFR_TMP_INIT (up, u, (mpfr_prec_t) un * GMP_NUMB_BITS, un);
51 MPFR_TMP_INIT (vp, v, (mpfr_prec_t) vn * GMP_NUMB_BITS, vn);
52
53 mpfr_ubf_mul_exact (u, a, b);
54 mpfr_ubf_mul_exact (v, c, d);
55 if (neg)
56 MPFR_CHANGE_SIGN (v);
57 if (prec_z == MPFR_PREC(a) && prec_z == MPFR_PREC(b) &&
58 prec_z == MPFR_PREC(c) && prec_z == MPFR_PREC(d) &&
59 un == MPFR_PREC2LIMBS(2 * prec_z))
60 {
61 MPFR_TMP_INIT (zp, zz, 2 * prec_z, un);
62 MPFR_PREC(u) = MPFR_PREC(v) = 2 * prec_z;
63 inex = mpfr_add (zz, (mpfr_srcptr) u, (mpfr_srcptr) v, rnd);
64 inex = mpfr_set_1_2 (z, zz, rnd, inex);
65 }
66 else
67 inex = mpfr_add (z, (mpfr_srcptr) u, (mpfr_srcptr) v, rnd);
68
69 MPFR_UBF_CLEAR_EXP (u);
70 MPFR_UBF_CLEAR_EXP (v);
71
72 MPFR_TMP_FREE (marker);
73
74 return inex;
75}
76
77/* z <- a*b + c*d */
78int
79mpfr_fmma (mpfr_ptr z, mpfr_srcptr a, mpfr_srcptr b, mpfr_srcptr c,
80 mpfr_srcptr d, mpfr_rnd_t rnd)
81{
82 return mpfr_fmma_aux (z, a, b, c, d, rnd, 0);
83}
84
85/* z <- a*b - c*d */
86int
87mpfr_fmms (mpfr_ptr z, mpfr_srcptr a, mpfr_srcptr b, mpfr_srcptr c,
88 mpfr_srcptr d, mpfr_rnd_t rnd)
89{
90 return mpfr_fmma_aux (z, a, b, c, d, rnd, 1);
91}
